{"tid":2150930,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葵涌碼頭群組增至10人","createTime":"2020-08-11T06:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T06:51:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b76d71589c6c309726a7a67d30a03c141075b443","tid":2150930,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:51:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/YJWHNPCODRPB2OHKEJP4MD57CQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2FYJWHNPCODRPB2OHKEJP4MD57CQ%2F&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lI26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=3418c379\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2FYJWHNPCODRPB2OHKEJP4MD57CQ%2F&h=44647ae4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/YJWHNPCODRPB2OHKEJP4MD57CQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n葵涌碼頭群組增至10人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hbtgfIheuSY0SET9DCawkj_2sbg=/190x112/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Z7IVP6DOHBXTSM4C2D437B6CVA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhbtgfIheuSY0SET9DCawkj_2sbg%3D%2F190x112%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZ7IVP6DOHBXTSM4C2D437B6CVA.jpg&h=343d9b48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葵涌碼頭群組增至十人染疫，當局估計休息室或更衣場所為播毒地點。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】疫情持續於不同行業蔓延。葵涌貨櫃碼頭群組昨新增兩人確診，令群組感染人數增至十人。衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君相信，病毒是有關人員在休息室及更衣間傳播。至於早前確診的有線新聞部攝影師，與他密切接觸的一名女記者昨亦確診。<br />\n<br />\n葵涌貨櫃碼頭群組再多兩人確診，涉及一名58歲男病人（4090號個案），與早。。。。。。。。。 。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有線實習女記者確診<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：拒受監察 推撞恫嚇總編輯<br />\n<br />\n有線電視證實新聞部再有人確診感染武漢肺炎，業界流傳為一名就讀於香港恒生大學的蔡姓實習女記者，有線電視昨回覆指，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n而康文署公佈，一名於香港動植物公園工作的女外判保安員前日確診，她最。。。。。。。。。。"}]}